text: Lottia fenestrata is a species of sea snail, a true limpet, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Lottiidae, one of the families of true limpets. ==Description== The shell can grow to be 20 mm to 38 mm ==Distribution== ==References== ==External links== * Category:Lottiidae Category:Gastropods described in 1855
title: Lottia fenestrata
